{"tid":1561944,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中國中出即飛，快入！！（認真文915英領事館）","createTime":"2019-09-11T21:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T10:41:37.000Z","uid":208927,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3dc40e7f3c5aafc95d8b4c8709ab3e138e0c5bde","tid":1561944,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T21:26:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">英國</span>被<span style=\"color: red;\">中</span>出<span style=\"color: blue;\">即飛</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n915除左民陣大遊行外都會有人上去英領事館<br />\n請願兩樣野：<br />\n1. 中英聯合聲明已經被無視要求英國政府採取行動<br />\n2. 承認一國兩制已遭受破壞<br />\n<br />\n好多時候大家都會屌英國，話英國冇撚用<br />\n中英聯合聲明同基本法一樣係笑話<br />\n都係共匪講大話偷利益、偷自由<br />\n不過平心而論，我地為BNO問題做左啲咩？<br />\nTwitter? 上連登屌？簽petition?<br />\nPetition 都係話要BNO轉BC<br />\n同大家講唔好發夢，唔好諗啲咩責任個套<br />\n然後叫英國送BC<br />\n<br />\n陶傑都講，呢場係場perfect storm<br />\n噤岩侵侵做pred, 又同中國打貿易戰<br />\n然後撞正香港反送中，美國先會「幫」香港噤多<br />\n大家都明白係各取所需，<br />\n如果對香港冇益，你都唔會拎美國旗唱<br />\nstar spangled banner<br />\n<br />\n英國同樣，喂大佬，有咩着數先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算排除利益，你愛英國咩？做乜要比BC你？<br />\n之前有個英領巴打話英國人好睇loyalty <br />\n點不知98之後真係有英國人問點解唔係唱英國國歌<br />\n問心，有幾個BNO識唱或仲記得英國國歌<br />\nOk, 其他愛國歌曲呢？你數得幾多首？<br />\n英國歷史你又知幾多？可能連邊4舊係英國<br />\nGreat Britain 冇北愛份你都唔知<br />\n<br />\n只要你真係鍾意英國，呢啲嘢你自然就識<br />\n所以其實我地咪又係利益撚，<br />\n我地都係攞英國著數，唉r兩r冇反應就唔要你<br />\n我宜家就去擁抱美帝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0SWXxRN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0SWXxRN.gif&h=2c49d93a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國人見到，睬你都有味<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地要同英國講，拎返香港(人)係好有益的！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\nStep 1: 915 拎英/香港旗唱爆God Save the Queen</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zppSl5bw2GU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzppSl5bw2GU&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=bca034d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zppSl5bw2GU</a><br />\n（2:00，地點為香港）<br />\n最少最少，都要認返契老母先<br />\n作為British empire 嘅最後一個殖民地<br />\n香港回歸其實係帝國滅亡，所以放假係黎默哀的<br />\n宜家英國脫歐，有一部份原因係想要重拾昔日光彩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人比你！</span></span><br />\n打比喻有個居港多年外藉人士因香港而自豪<br />\n然後一齊唱榮光歸香港嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你諗下如果啲親生仔見到老母個契仔噤孝順<br />\n(我希望係真喇，不過樣都要做喇至少）<br />\n自己都會留意你多啲，尊重你同當你一家人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\np.s 我同你講power to the people <br />\n啲英國議員都要選民票<br />\n你話點解唔幫你？因為唔符合國民利益<br />\n事頭婆係精神領袖，係冇實權㗎<br />\n英國人鍾意你，你先有機<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Step2: 同英國講經濟誘因</span></span><br />\n英國係全世界第7大gdp國家，但其實大部分來自英格蘭<br />\n但你知唔知，香港其實GDP比蘇格蘭同威爾斯加埋仲多200億美金<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nAeihLL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnAeihLL.png&h=10b2fed1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CzxDhLM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCzxDhLM.png&h=99898a82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LB3fjY6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLB3fjY6.png&h=1efe7f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老老柒柒我賺到錢就寜願交稅比英國都唔比港共<br />\n你比英國知道呢啲經濟效益應該係佢地嘅<br />\n而香港係脫歐後嘅經濟強心針<br />\n加上915後英國人如果對香港人產生好感<br />\n一定係本土有更多聲音<br />\n<br />\n方向1: 英國以中英聯合聲明被毀約為由要求取回香港而交涉<br />\n-&gt; 中國冇可能交出香港-&gt; 轉方向比BC<br />\n(如果英美用清債券質疑中國對香港擁有權，中國會口啞啞<br />\n不過聽講債券英國部份已還清？）<br />\n<br />\n方向2: 係本土令人明白香港有重大經濟價值-&gt; <br />\n將目光投向香港人身上-&gt; 香港人可以係本土發展刺激經濟<br />\n-&gt; 比BC<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Step 3: 讓英國知道香港人想當兵報答國家</span></span><br />\n亦都係目前已有可以取得BC方法之一<br />\n我同你講英國當兵可以好好玩<br />\n文宣可以話香港人想繼續serve 事頭婆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pw8bCBz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPw8bCBz.jpg&h=17d670e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖為HKMSC，香港仲有個royal Hong Kong regiment<br />\n接觸過一啲想參軍巴，勿相認<br />\n個重點係好多人過唔到背景審查<br />\n同英文水平唔太高<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比力啊大家<br />\n所以文宣亦可以叫英國寛鬆background check <br />\n比BNO holder 當兵<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\nStep 4: 搬女皇上檯</span></span><br />\n我指維多利亞女皇，即伊利沙伯嘅太嫲上檯<br />\n因為香港一開始(港島開埠初地區) 係叫域多利亞城<br />\n比英國人知原來共産黨落9英國同女皇面<br />\n可以做啲登你傷心嘅文宣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5byV4kB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5byV4kB.jpg&h=e91aa5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n例子姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得如果出黎效果好真係好開始<br />\n過往行動零星，目標太遠<br />\n宜家可以一步一步從呢2個清𥇦訴求開始<br />\n希望大家到時915可以學識唱呢兩首<br />\n由其係I vow to thee，呢首歌係為戰爭愛國歌曲<br />\n我覺得係英國境外都冇人唱<br />\n跪求文宣同所會上英領嘅人<br />\n多多宣傳呢一首<br />\n<br />\n1. God save the Queen <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/haI8HMjlE9s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhaI8HMjlE9s&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=7a1e1a6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/haI8HMjlE9s</a><br />\n小弟剪的<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. I vow to thee my country<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bvouc8Qs_MI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fbvouc8Qs_MI&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=95ec7e5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bvouc8Qs_MI</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n915見<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"f3ed17ab2d080c10c1f7ac768a455549c9071e56","tid":1561944,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T21:26:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f054c6e8e9a5ae3133b02d15917bfa4ba3ac8555","tid":1561944,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T21:27:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0423b2add35cf6dae5020039dd4fdb80f8a5670","tid":1561944,"uid":208927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T21:27:33.000Z","msg":"Up<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人未瞓阿"},{"pid":"e583b4a1570819b6c6c76803ecf3ec26c74a1922","tid":1561944,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:23:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"91758ee01b5b8fa3345b729c4726704f89d53f90","tid":1561944,"uid":10778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6980d5fe9040d207d0ff8f94f04008d4e109cb73","tid":1561944,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91758ee01b5b8fa3345b729c4726704f89d53f90","tid":1561944,"uid":10778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:30:31.000Z","msg":"國家機密日前你就噤放上連登？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e59c620588d453ace65f665cb74197b0dc71282","tid":1561944,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6980d5fe9040d207d0ff8f94f04008d4e109cb73","tid":1561944,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91758ee01b5b8fa3345b729c4726704f89d53f90","tid":1561944,"uid":10778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:30:31.000Z","msg":"國家機密日前你就噤放上連登？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:30:54.000Z","msg":"Typo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eff734f09e2bf344af70a3abf62bd520295a058","tid":1561944,"uid":33970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:35:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d3ca12d8e950f2c9d94dce6cf9b040d953e7a5e","tid":1561944,"uid":281857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:38:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03fb160dfdc0e1a3f0607c0d08097d59ff24f70e","tid":1561944,"uid":255030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:40:05.000Z","msg":"屌你老母我推"},{"pid":"925dfab7961c2c82746578ee867212c5ca3088a0","tid":1561944,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:44:27.000Z","msg":"你地班漢奸又想做咩呀"},{"pid":"0df34bf4779c5fff4d0260fd3869aa5788945419","tid":1561944,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:45:33.000Z","msg":"睇黎香港好危險喎<br />\n香港咁多漢奸既"},{"pid":"4be8287f33b90f42b9386bab8930a50a9b8105a8","tid":1561944,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:54:51.000Z","msg":"😪<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e7f22652012fc096eabb3b14454a1530c7403f","tid":1561944,"uid":104592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T23:23:15.000Z","msg":"英國戰線都要做好佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a8cec221b47b265db2787a883d7d5262b930c1","tid":1561944,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:09:57.000Z","msg":"願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiW8u64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiW8u64.jpg&h=6e2a8a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558977</a>"},{"pid":"befefa5b9a8a68b31e151109fdcfe0b363206d71","tid":1561944,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"d0423b2add35cf6dae5020039dd4fdb80f8a5670","tid":1561944,"uid":208927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T21:27:33.000Z","msg":"Up<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人未瞓阿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6820e14d17ba285eff9ac695a50828b6dc9ec5","tid":1561944,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae7fd794938a969d5eb8789dc428799fbf3996e","tid":1561944,"uid":101537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VCKVnJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVCKVnJY.jpg&h=953198b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/18iyTQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18iyTQE.jpg&h=ba22aa39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12點有英領請願 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇下有冇得merge 下<br />\n<br />\n呢到有3000人channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/BritonsinHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FBritonsinHK&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=3e76b5d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/BritonsinHK</a>"},{"pid":"ec90d6df583c277092047dcd6e3f2135545d02b2","tid":1561944,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b73fc2a64b0e151d293c195b9580a73a00d00c","tid":1561944,"uid":69646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:41:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5adc3df6b3f5a126f76c22b5dab045fdbd2dac28","tid":1561944,"uid":69646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:42:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5beb3a92b0058a396d6e3d77e7fd4fe67b8ec3b","tid":1561944,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:42:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6abe44a4ddb3b05da3483e0549a3bb64e4cf9dda","tid":1561944,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:09:23.000Z","msg":"有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369cc0d15b627bb8517ac4c8cc72f87fd30933c8","tid":1561944,"uid":206466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}